query:
SELECT 
  i.id,
  wl.code AS endereco,
  p.sku,
  p.description,
  i.batch AS lote,
  i.quantity AS qtd_total,
  i.reservedQuantity AS qtd_reservada,
  (i.quantity - i.reservedQuantity) AS qtd_disponivel
FROM inventory i
LEFT JOIN warehouseLocations wl ON i.locationId = wl.id
LEFT JOIN products p ON i.productId = p.id
WHERE i.reservedQuantity > 0
ORDER BY i.updatedAt DESC
LIMIT 10;
